info.+content: Log Horizon: Destruction of the Round Table
ログ・ホライズン 円卓崩壊

It's been a year since Shiroe and his friends were trapped in Akiba due to the Catastrophe. Their forging of the Round Table has brought order and prosperity to its people. But fracturing political alliances and the constant menace of the Genius monsters threaten to destabilize all they've fought for and built.
